- [gunshots]

18
00:01:12,291 --> 00:01:14,207
[sheriff speaks indistinctly]

19
00:01:14,208 --> 00:01:16,374
- [deputy indistinct]
- [sheriff indistinct]

20
00:01:16,375 --> 00:01:18,582
